csdl.jupiter.model.review
Class ReviewModel

java.lang.Object
  csdl.jupiter.model.review.ReviewModel

public class ReviewModel
extends java.lang.Object

Provides review model. Clients may get the singleton instance. All get's methods are guaranteed to return non-null and updated information. This may used to retrieved the review issue model through ReviewIssueManager, the column data model through ColumnDataModelManager.

Version:
$Id: ReviewModel.java,v 1.10 2005/03/28 14:39:31 takuyay Exp $

Takuya Yamashita
